DEF
CRI AND
CTN textfilecontent54
    TEST `at least one exists` all
    OBJECT obj_1001
        path `/etc/chrony`
        filename `.*\.conf`
        pattern `^\s*makestep\s+1\s+-1\s*`
        instance `1`
    OBJECT_END
CTN_END
CTN shellcommand
    TEST `at least one exists` all
    STATE ste_1002
        exit_status int equals `0`
        stdout_line string equals `\s*System\s+clock\s+synchronized:\s+yes`
    STATE_END
    OBJECT obj_1002
        shell `bash`
        command `timedatectl | grep -Ei 'synchronized' `
        pattern `.*`
    OBJECT_END
CTN_END
CTN shellcommand
    TEST `at least one exists` all
    STATE ste_1003
        exit_status int equals `0`
        stdout_line string equals `\s*NTP\s+service:\s+active`
    STATE_END
    OBJECT obj_1003
        shell `bash`
        command `timedatectl | grep -Ei 'service' `
        pattern `.*`
    OBJECT_END
CTN_END
CRI_END
DEF_END